verse.lines:
I've been blessed
with many things,
God's been good to me;
I have family and friends
Who share in all I do;

He's the only reason I live
But oh, what a reason;
He's the only reason I live
But oh, what a reason;

You may have tried
a whole lot of things
To find real happiness;
But if you look very long,
then you'll know
That it just cannot be found;
